data.text:
Originally released in 1960, Ella Wishes You A Swinging Christmas is one of the greatest Christmas albums ever made, and it never ages. Ella, along with a studio orchestra conducted by Frank DeVol, puts her unique stamp on popular Christmas songs including Jingle Bells, Santa Claus Is Coming To Town, Have Yourself A Merry Christmas and many more (12 tracks in total).

TRACKLISTING

1. Jingle Bells

2. Santa Claus Is Coming To Town

3. Have Yourself A Merry Little Christmas

4. What Are You Doing New Year's Eve?

5. Sleigh Ride

6. The Christmas Song

7. Good Morning Blues

8. Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow!

9. Winter Wonderland

10. Rudolph The Red-Nosed Reindeer

11. Frosty The Snow Man

12. White Christmas
